data.description: If you've ever dreamed of owning a lake house, here's your chance! Come home to this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath home that backs up to a view of Cherry Lake. Enjoy the privacy and beautiful serenity of nature while sitting out on your deck with a cold beverage of your choice and throwing some steaks on the grill. The half acre of land allows for plenty of room to roam and play in the fenced backyard, so you'll have ample space from your side neighbors and no rear neighbors. It is located only minutes from the Turnpike, which makes commuting to work a breeze. The kitchen features granite countertops, a stylish backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a bay window to allow for plenty of natural light. The home has tile throughout the kitchen and large great room, laminate wood flooring in the bedrooms, and ceiling fans throughout. The owner's suite features a dual vanity, large walk in closet, stand up shower and a garden tub with a window for more natural light. The home comes with the washer and dryer, as well as solar panels on the roof to save on your power bill. This is an amazing deal on such a rare property with an oversized lot and lake access. Make your appointment today!
